{"id":963426063,"question_id":2838,"lang":"java","lang_name":"Java","time":"1Â year","timestamp":1685852406,"status":10,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"22 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/963426063/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Sum of Matrix After Queries","memory":"75.1 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    public long matrixSumQueries(int n, int[][] queries) {\n        long row=n,col=n;\n        long sum=0;\n        HashSet<Integer> rowMap=new HashSet<>();\n        HashSet<Integer> colMap=new HashSet<>();\n        for(int i=queries.length-1;i>=0;i--){\n            if(queries[i][0]==0){\n                if(col<=0||rowMap.contains(queries[i][1]))continue;\n                sum+=(col)*(long)queries[i][2];\n                rowMap.add(queries[i][1]);\n                row--;\n            }else{\n                if(row<=0||colMap.contains(queries[i][1]))continue;\n                sum+=(row)*(long)queries[i][2];\n                colMap.add(queries[i][1]);\n                col--;\n            }\n        }\n        return sum;\n    }\n}","compare_result":"","title_slug":"sum-of-matrix-after-queries","has_notes":false,"flag_type":1}
